OL,3,CRyanair passenger partially sucked out
OL,4,Cof broken window, reports claim
OL,6,FA Ryanair passenger was reportedly
OL,7,Fpartially sucked out of a plane window
OL,8,Fwhich shattered in mid-air.
OL,10,FThe incident involved a Boeing 737-800
OL,11,Faircraft which departed the Greek city
OL,12,FThessaloniki at 6.01am local time on
OL,13,FFriday, bound for Memmingen, Germany.
OL,15,FLocal media in Greece reported the
OL,16,Fvictim was a Serbian man aged in his
OL,17,F60s, whose head was sucked out of the
OL,18,Fwindow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
