OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783718417
OL,3,CRyanair passenger partially sucked out
OL,4,Cof broken window, reports claim
OL,6,FOther passengers were able to pull him
OL,7,Fback into the cabin after several
OL,8,Fminutes, according to reports, which
OL,9,Falso stated the window was shattered
OL,10,Fwhen an engine part broke off.
OL,12,FFootage of the aftermath of the
OL,13,Fincident from inside the cabin,
OL,14,Fobtained by Radio Thessaloniki in
OL,15,FGreece, shows the shattered window and
OL,16,Freleased oxygen masks.
