OL,3,CRyanair passenger partially sucked out
OL,4,Cof broken window, reports claim
OL,6,FRyanair said in a statement: "A
OL,7,FRyanair flight from Thessaloniki to
OL,8,FMemmingen on Friday morning (10 July)
OL,9,Freturned to Thessaloniki shortly after
OL,10,Ftake-off when a passenger window
OL,11,Fdislodged inflight.
OL,13,F"The aircraft landed normally and
OL,14,Fpassengers returned to the terminal.
OL,15,FOne passenger requested and received
OL,16,Fmedical assistance on the ground in
OL,17,FThessaloniki.
OL,26,@nD@^OU
