OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783718417
OL,3,CRyanair passenger partially sucked out
OL,4,Cof broken window, reports claim
OL,6,F"In order to minimise any delay, a
OL,7,Freplacement aircraft was arranged to
OL,8,Fbring passengers to Memmingen which
OL,9,Fdeparted Thessaloniki at 9:53 local
OL,10,Fthis morning.
OL,12,FFlight tracking website Flightradar24
OL,13,Fshows the plane began to turn around
OL,14,Fafter about 22 minutes in the air.
OL,16,FIt then burned fuel at low altitude
OL,17,Ffor about half an hour before landing
OL,18,Fone hour and 15 minutes after take-off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
