OL,3,CRyanair passenger partially sucked out
OL,4,Cof broken window, reports claim
OL,6,FThe plane has Ryanair livery but was
OL,7,Foperated by Malta Air, a subsidiary of
OL,8,Fthe Irish company.
OL,10,FA replacement aircraft departed
OL,11,FThessaloniki at 9.53am local time.
